Step 5 – Replace Auth0 placeholder client IDs
In deploy-blazor-apps.yml:

Line with STAGING_CLIENT_ID → replace with the Manager app's client_id from rvs-staging.us.auth0.com
Line with PROD_CLIENT_ID → replace with the Manager app's client_id from rvs.us.auth0.com
Both values are public OIDC client IDs (safe to commit; required for PKCE flow). Do this after Auth0 tenant provisioning when you have the client IDs.